name: Craft panel :: 1966 Foden S36
description:
I love old trucks and love to draw them just as much.
They all have such different personalities it's hard not to love them.

This craft panel is one of my original designs. 
Use it in a cushion cover, quilt, drawstring bag or make a simple softie... perfect for the little old truck lover in your life.

Digitally printed using eco-friendly inks on a linen/cotton base.
Approximately 22cm x 22cm (8.5" x 8.5"). 


Cool machine wash with a phosphate free detergent. Air dry.
